title: [SOLVED]820-3115-B LED fades to none and only after battery disconnect shows indication.
message:
[PLAIN][SOLVED]820-3115-B LED fades to none and only after battery disconnect shows indication.[/PLAIN]

I replaced dcin, magsafe and battery and same symptoms..
only after disconnecting battery and attaching magsafe and battery back i get sometimes indication lights but it fades very slowly to 0, if I cover LED i can see very weak green light pulsing.
no corrosion.

title: [SOLVED]820-3115-B LED fades to none and only after battery disconnect shows indication.
message:
So you mean there is no green light? Battery is not needed for this and can be left disconnected for now.
What is you PPBUS voltage? 12.3 or 12.6?

title: [SOLVED]820-3115-B LED fades to none and only after battery disconnect shows indication.
message: Well since it was intermittent I gave it a good bath and the baby stopped crying..thanks.
